			<p>
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">this quest can be done by geting &lt;Three&gt; bear hide pelts from diffarnt bears in (E-comms).<BR>
You need a low quality bear hide for the &lt;&lt;Bear hide belt&gt;&gt;...You need a medium quality bear pelt for the &lt;&lt;bear hide cloke&gt;&gt; and you need a HIGH qualityy bear plet for the &lt;&lt;Bear hide boots &gt;&gt; very cool item<BR>
After you get these pelts then travel to QEYNOS Hills and follow the trail to the castel...There be for you go into the castel you will see two peeps by a fire ...Go hail them and they will tell you what to give them for the stuff.<BR>
You willl need to do this fast though becasue peeps have been killing the girl and boy for the loot...&lt;&lt;,GOOD $&gt;&gt; :)<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
((Oho yea....you will have to pay like 22gp for each item also...give the pelt and the money at the same time)))<BR>
GOOD luck in your jurnies and your travels to quenoy...this is a VERY good quest for casters like me..&gt;:) <BR>
PeAcE OUT!:)
